This paper discusses the CleverHans library, which is primarily focused on adversarial examples in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses attacks and defenses, which are related to computer security (cs.CR). Additionally, the library has applications in computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE).
